pull_request.title: Add numbers to CPU and memory bars.
pull_request.body: This PR adds numbers to bars to avoid the need to mouse over entries (though that tooltip functionality remains). To ensure that labels fit, numbers only appear on segments comprising at least 20% of the total. The screenshot below presents an example profile with the new functionality. Partially addresses https://github.com/plasma-umass/scalene/issues/717.
